token.name: Eclipse Dragon
token.description: Forged from starlight and shadows, the Eclipse Dragon emerges only during celestial alignments. Its obsidian scales shimmer with constellations, and its breath holds the power to bend time and space. Legends say that those who possess its essence gain unparalleled wisdom—though at the cost of fleeting moments lost to the void. Will you dare wield its mystic force?
